of the synthesis run by clicking below to browse all of the synthesis runs that have been completed.</p>
<a href="/v3/tree_of_life/browse_custom"><input type="button" value="Browse runs" /></a>
<br />
<div class="footnote"></div>
<script>
var custom_server = "{{canonical_url}}";
var ini_ott = "{{ott}}";
var ini_collection = "{{collection}}";
</script>
